<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَهُمْ الذِينَ قَدْ أَكْثَرُوا مِنْ ذِكْرِهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فِي السِّرِّ وَالإِعْلانِ وَالأَحْيَانِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يَتَقَرَّبُونَ إِلى الْمَلِيكِ بِفِعْلِهِمْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>طَاعَاتِهِ وَالتَّرْكِ لِلْعِصْيَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَعْلُ الْفَرَائِضِ وَالنَّوَافِلِ دَأْبُهُمْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>مَعْ رُؤْيَةِ التَّقْصِيرِ وَالنُّقْصَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>صَبَّرُوا النُّفُوسَ عَلَى الْمَكَارِهِ كُلِّهَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>شَوْقًا إِلى مَا فِيهِ مِنْ إِحْسَانِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>نَزَلُوا بِمَنْزِلَةِ الرِّضَى فَهُمُوا بِهَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>قَدْ أَصْبَحُوا فِي جُنَّةِِ وَأَمَانِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>شَكَرُوا الذِي أَوْلَى الْخَلائِقَ فَضْلَهُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بِالْقَلْب وَالأَقْوَالِ وَالأَرْكَانِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>صَحِبُوا التَّوَكُّلَ فِي جَمِيعِ أَمُورِهِمْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>مَعْ بَذْلِ جُهْدٍ فِي رِضَى الرَّحْمَانِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>عَبَدُوا الإِلهَ عَلَى اعْتِقَادِ حُضُورِهِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَتَبَوَّءوُا فِي مَنْزِلِ الإِحْسَانِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>نَصَحُوا الْخَلِيقَةَ فِي رِضَى مَحْبُوبِهِمْ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>بِالْعِلْمِ وَالإِرْشَادِ وَالإِحْسَانِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>صَحِبُوا الْخَلائِقَ بِالْجُسُومِ وَإِنَّمَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>أَرْوَاحُهُمْ فِي مَنْزِلٍ فَوْقَانِي<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>